  "detailed_description": "<div class=\"bb_code\">This game is not for everyone. Please try the demo before buying, your progress will carry over.</div><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>We have gone through hell and back to acquire the SWARM software used by Terranos Engineering. Help us figure out its nefarious purposes.</strong></h2><br>Know your enemy, explore features of the software that are listed below:<br><br><strong>A.cquire</strong><br><i>Earn</i> parts, decals, badges, and titles by completing missions and competing in PvP seasons.<br><br><strong>B.uild</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131150/extras/cbe84444e83878cc2c64441396535867.poster.avif?t=1771539822\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131150/extras/cbe84444e83878cc2c64441396535867.webm?t=1771539822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131150/extras/cbe84444e83878cc2c64441396535867.mp4?t=1771539822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Design</i> a custom drone from a variety of parts. Adjust attachment locations and angles to produce ultimate killing machines. Change part colors and add decals for a bit of personal touch.<br><br><strong>C.ode</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131150/extras/b8647589559271d815d0c3662f4118d1.poster.avif?t=1771539822\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131150/extras/b8647589559271d815d0c3662f4118d1.webm?t=1771539822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131150/extras/b8647589559271d815d0c3662f4118d1.mp4?t=1771539822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Program</i> each part of your drone with a custom visual programming interface.<br><br><strong>D.eploy</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131150/extras/c6425dca3e6252e07828c26898d7ed00.poster.avif?t=1771539822\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131150/extras/c6425dca3e6252e07828c26898d7ed00.webm?t=1771539822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131150/extras/c6425dca3e6252e07828c26898d7ed00.mp4?t=1771539822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Send your drones on various <i>missions</i> to earn rewards, with different goals in each level. Try to beat your fastest time.<br><br><strong>E.valuate</strong><br>Submit and play custom missions crafted by fellow engineers.<br><br><strong>F.launt</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131150/extras/d52e7517ba9e619764f3020ff49b15f3.poster.avif?t=1771539822\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131150/extras/d52e7517ba9e619764f3020ff49b15f3.webm?t=1771539822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131150/extras/d52e7517ba9e619764f3020ff49b15f3.mp4?t=1771539822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Show off your creations against other engineers in <i>asynchronous PvP</i> battles. Your opponents do not have to be online to be challenged. Participate in different modes, such as 1v1 or a 6 drone free-for-all battle. Earn rating to climb the seasonal leaderboards.<br><br><strong>G.auge</strong><br>Participate in <i>tournaments</i>  to see if your team can come out on top.<br><br><strong>H.ave</strong><br><i>Fun</i>",
